sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Cam as 摄像头帧源
participant AppUI as AppUI流式回调
participant Pipeline as PlatePipeline
participant YOLO as YoloDetector
participant OCR as OcrRecognizer
participant Cache as CooldownCache
participant VIP as VipStore
participant Logger as HistoryLogger
participant FS as 文件系统(CSV/Images)

loop 每一帧
  Cam->>AppUI: frame
  AppUI->>Pipeline: process_image(frame, flip, is_stream=true)
  Pipeline->>YOLO: detect(frame, conf=0.5)
  YOLO-->>Pipeline: boxes

  loop 每个检测框
    Pipeline->>OCR: recognize(cropped_plate)
    OCR-->>Pipeline: plate_text
    Pipeline->>VIP: contains(plate_text)
    VIP-->>Pipeline: is_marked
    Pipeline->>Cache: should_save(plate_text, now)

    alt 首次出现或超过5秒
      Cache-->>Pipeline: true
      Pipeline->>Logger: save_capture(...)
      Logger->>FS: 写入图片
      Pipeline->>Logger: append_csv(row)
      Logger->>FS: 写入CSV
      Pipeline->>Cache: touch(plate_text, now)
    else 5秒内重复车牌
      Cache-->>Pipeline: false
      Pipeline->>Pipeline: 仅渲染，不入库
    end
  end

  Pipeline-->>AppUI: 返回渲染帧与文本
end
